sentence: what is the length of the colorado river in texas ?
sentence-with-vars: what is the length of the river0 in state0 ?
sql: select river.length from river where river.river_name = ' colorado ' and river.traverse = ' texas ' ;
sql-with-vars: select river.length from river where river.river_name = ' river0 ' and river.traverse = ' state0 ' ;
